- Vibration: <25 µm/s (VC-E curve)
- EMI Shielding: 100 dB attenuation (DC to 10 GHz)

Compute Resources:
Quantum:
- 128,000 physical qubits (mixed technologies)
- 128 logical qubits (d=31 surface code)
- 10⁹ logical operations per second
- <10⁻¹⁵ logical error rate per operation

Neuromorphic:
- 1 trillion neurons
- 256 trillion synapses
- 10¹² spikes per second
- 5 pJ per spike energy efficiency

Classical Co-processing:
- 1 exaflops (FP64) conventional HPC
- 4 petabytes unified memory
- 1 exabyte NVMe-over-Fabric storage
- 400 Gbps InfiniBand fabric

Network Connectivity:
- Optical: 100 Tbps to other Tier 0 hubs
- Quantum: Entanglement distribution at 1 kHz
- 6G: Direct connection to core network
- Satellite: Quantum key distribution links
```

