10. Appendices

Appendix A: Technical Glossary

Quantum Terms:

· Logical Qubit: Error-corrected qubit composed of many physical qubits
· Surface Code: A 2D quantum error correcting code with high threshold
· T₁, T₂: Coherence times for quantum information
· NISQ: Noisy Intermediate-Scale Quantum (current era of quantum computing)

Neuromorphic Terms:

· LIF Neuron: Leaky Integrate-and-Fire neuron model
· STDP: Spike-Timing-Dependent Plasticity (biological learning rule)
· AER: Address-Event Representation (communication protocol for spikes)
· NeuroCore: Hardware unit implementing neuromorphic computation

6G Terms:

· RIS: Reconfigurable Intelligent Surface (programmable metasurface)
· THz: Terahertz frequencies (100 GHz - 10 THz)
· JCAS: Joint Communication and Sensing
· Network Slicing: Virtual networks with dedicated resources

